name: Vanguard Canadian Corporate Bond Index ETF
longDescription: The investment objective of Vanguard Canadian Corporate Bond Index ETF the ETF is to track, to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses, the performance of the Bloomberg Global Aggregate Canadian Corporate Float Adjusted Bond Index the Index or the Benchmark.
fulldescription: The investment objective of Vanguard Canadian Corporate Bond Index ETF the ETF is to track, to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses, the performance of the Bloomberg Global Aggregate Canadian Corporate Float Adjusted Bond Index the Index or the Benchmark. To achieve its investment objective, the ETF employs a passive management, or indexing, investment approach designed to track the performance of the Index by holding a broadly diversified subset of securities that, in the aggregate, approximates the full Index in terms of primary risk factors, including duration, yield, quality, sector distribution and issue exposure, as well as other key characteristics of the Index
